query:
SELECT id, emailType, recipientEmail, subject, sentAt, errorMessage 
FROM email_logs 
WHERE recipientEmail = 'e2e-test-jan5@launchbase-test.com' 
AND emailType = 'intake_confirmation'
ORDER BY sentAt DESC 
LIMIT 1;
